   <p>
    12/4/18 — Read Lu's
    <a href="https://www.pnas.org/content/115/49/E11475.short">
     new paper
    </a>
    in PNAS using molecular
dynamics to study the catalytic cycle in KaiC. We show how KaiA can act as a nucleotide exchange factor by destabilizng the KaiC subunit interfaces.
   </p>
